{"type": "article", "id": 26101, "title": "手制皮革钱包", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-28T07:10:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702152258CM1UNE6ouFTzbWBR.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://pufftec.com/products/pufftec-wallet\">Fumo Wallet</a> 是夏威夷品牌 PuffTec 针对卷烟爱好者推出的一款手制皮革钱包。即便你无意放入卷烟装备，各类丰富的夹层和口袋不仅美观，也能满足你其他的收纳需求（比方说，它是以一台 iPhone 6 尺寸所设计的，完全可以用作手机套）。钱包采用的是意大利进口的皮革，每只售价为 300 美元。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070215225241ANSLkVaH5YDhfB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152252OvyWHohTa63lcgiz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021522562QUbFYN6rByvhPq4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021522567Zvp1coPU2g3EHna.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}